value.content: The transportId property uniquely identifies the RTCIceTransport that was inspected to obtain the transport-related statistics contained in the RTCIceCandidatePairStats object.

value.title: Value
value.content:
A string which uniquely identifies the RTCIceTransport object from which the transport-related data was obtained for the statistics contained in this RTCIceCandidatePairStats object.

The transport-related statistics come from the RTCTransportStats dictionary's properties.
